        alt="Physical AI in Healthcare — Stronger together. Healthier tomorrow. A nurse and a humanoid robot care for an elderly patient in a New Zealand hospital, with displays showing fleet learning across a network of robots and the message that augmenting human care reduces workload and delivers better outcomes."
